title: Protein-Packed Breakfast Classics Order ships & arrives separately | 22 Servings
description: Your order will ship separately from your HF meals and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.

Enjoy this bundle of protein-packed breakfasts, perfectly portioned for convenience.

Start your day off right with two of **Elmhurst’s Toasted Vanilla Almond Lattes** with cold brew coffee- ***4g protein per serving (4 servings).***

Next, there are **Three Cheese & Spinach Protein Cakes from Crepini**, made with simple ingredients and containing ***12 grams of protein per serving (4 servings).***

Also from Crepini there are **Omelets To-Go, filled with cheddar cheese and sausage** for a ***16-gram boost of protein per serving (4 servings).***

Bagels are always a breakfast favorite, and these delights from **Sola** feature ***15 grams of protein per bagel (4 servings) with only 5 grams of net carbs.***

And because you’ll need a topping for the bagels, we’ve included four single-serve packets of **Philadelphia Cream Cheese**  ***(1.3g protein per serving).***

Finally, we’re sending **Overnight Oats from Mush.** The peanut butter flavor packs ***15 grams of protein per serving (2 servings).***
