== Crepini Three Cheese and Spinach Protein Cakes ==

Remove @Crepini Three Cheese and Spinach Protein Rounds{2} from packaging.

Microwave until heated through, ~{15-20%seconds}.

== Crepini Sausage and Cheddar Wrap-Ups ==

Remove @Crepini Sausage and Cheddar Wrap Ups{2} from packaging.

Microwave until heated through, ~{25-30%seconds}.

== Elmhurst Almond Vanilla Latte ==

Enjoy @Elmhurst Almond Vanilla Latte{2}.

== Sola Bagel ==

Keep @Sola Bagel Plain{1}(frozen) until ready to eat. (Do not microwave.)

OVEN OR TOASTER OVEN: Preheat #oven{} to 425 degrees. Place on a #baking sheet{}; bake until golden brown, ~{7-10%minutes}. (Note: Oven times may vary.)

AIR FRYER: Arrange bagels side by side in an #air fryer basket{} (you may have to work in batches). Air-fry at 400 degrees until golden brown, ~{4-5%minutes}. (Note: Air fryer times may vary).

Let cool ~{2-3%minutes}, then slice and spread with as much @Philadelphia Cream Cheese{4%single-serve packets} as you like.

== Mush Peanut Butter Overnight Oats ==

Enjoy @Mush Peanut Butter Overnight Oats{2}.